subSubSection.paragraph:
Female (
paratype
): Female larger (L = 3455 µm) but similar to male in general body shape. One posterior ovary located on the right side of intestine, antidromously reflexed. Vulval orifice ventral, located at 20% of body length. Uterus and oviduct 2675 µm long and the antidromously reflexed ovary 200 µm in length. Vagina short and not thickened.
